{"tid":711094,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"微軟利用 AI 來提供更流暢的 Windows 10 更新體驗","createTime":"2018-06-21T09:23:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-21T14:58:56.000Z","uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"51ceaddf4863191a7a59ca541e04ea6ca25eb5e7","tid":711094,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T09:23:42.000Z","msg":"AI 技術已經廣泛應用到不同的生活細節，但你有沒有想過就連電腦系統的更新過程都有 AI 幫助呢？微軟在部落格上發佈文章指，他們為 Windows 10 裝置的更新過程加入了 AI，讓整個體驗更流暢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://chinese.engadget.com/2018/06/14/microsoft-ai-windows-10-updates-smoother/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchinese.engadget.com%2F2018%2F06%2F14%2Fmicrosoft-ai-windows-10-updates-smoother%2F&d=TIjPz5sjqPVI6l%2FEJ%2BrCdMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=fb5e5cb1\" target=\"_blank\">https://chinese.engadget.com/2018/06/14/microsoft-ai-windows-10-updates-smoother/</a>"},{"pid":"a29ac573f5fc833eae2aaa59c6412920c6c0a0ff","tid":711094,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T09:25:47.000Z","msg":"據文章的說法，微軟其實已經在之前的 Windows 10 Fall Creators Update 推送過程中嘗試加入 AI 的幫忙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，讓 AI 模型能分析裝置和儘早把更新推送<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。微軟最後發現由 AI 系統推送的更新獲得更高的客戶滿意度<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，也較少需要透過電話來協助解難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，所以就在 Windows 10 April 2018 更新的過程中再次應用 AI 系統<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。而且這次更錄得了 Windows 10 更新版本之中，使用最少時間就推送至 2.5 億台機器之上的記錄<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，比較 Fall Creators Update 節省了一半的時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。"},{"pid":"ba9ab313c3496827fe1e507d919aca9c28dad5f7","tid":711094,"uid":65012,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T09:32:58.000Z","msg":"Update送rootkit<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(PS 9up)"},{"pid":"cb82be4b8210387306256c053c934fe6f6f0fd2e","tid":711094,"uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ba9ab313c3496827fe1e507d919aca9c28dad5f7","tid":711094,"uid":65012,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T09:32:58.000Z","msg":"Update送rootkit<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(PS 9up)"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T11:35:11.000Z","msg":"用AI收集個人資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbeb08a00c5816e8072d476e384662944661972e","tid":711094,"uid":162421,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T13:56:02.000Z","msg":"Windows update既時間足以睇場波"},{"pid":"0a6fdf709054a034c26ee7301ab19cd8062be7c3","tid":711094,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"cb82be4b8210387306256c053c934fe6f6f0fd2e","tid":711094,"uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ba9ab313c3496827fe1e507d919aca9c28dad5f7","tid":711094,"uid":65012,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T09:32:58.000Z","msg":"Update送rootkit<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(PS 9up)"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T11:35:11.000Z","msg":"用AI收集個人資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T14:58:56.000Z","msg":"以前冇 AI 已經流暢<br />\n而家有 AI 先可以流暢"}]}